5ZXmwg">Nguyễn Phúc Hồng Vịnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Quan-ng%E1%BA%A3i-m%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-JzWlxPd-lE47NsallWLHWQ">Quan ngải mạch - 觀刈麥</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thi%E1%BB%81n-am-t%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BB%B1u/poem-wVwEZsJUGtPVUMf_6981dw">Thiền am tự cựu - 禪庵寺舊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ti%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BB%ADu/poem-1QyYtj392U9KThUlfaehoA">Thương tiến tửu - 將進酒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-CZQp1s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Y%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A0i-thi-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/poem-Q_VyLgbhjqEGgyO1NHSMRw">Yên đài thi - Đông - 燕臺詩－冬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
